---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Medical Marijuana Costs in Florida | Releaf MD" 
  description="Break down the costs of Florida medical marijuana cards, including doctor evaluation fees, state registry charges, and dispensary pricing."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-brand-mint py-16 lg:py-24 border-b border-brand-primary/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-4">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-brand-primary/10 text-brand-primary rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
        💰 Pricing Breakdown
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark leading-tight uppercase">Florida Medical Marijuana Costs</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Get a transparent overview of evaluation fees, annual state registry costs, and general retail product price expectations.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white border border-brand-primary/10 rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-whisper prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8">
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">How much does a medical marijuana evaluation cost in Florida?</h2>
        <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 border border-brand-primary/20 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center my-6">
          <p class="text-4xl font-serif-headline font-black text-brand-primary mb-2">$150.00 to $200.00</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Typical Price Range for Initial Certifications</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          In Florida, a medical marijuana doctor evaluation typically costs between <strong>$150.00 and $200.00</strong> for an initial certification, and <strong>$100.00 to $150.00</strong> for subsequent 30-week renewal cycles. Because health insurance does not cover medical cannabis or clinical evaluation fees, these charges must be paid directly to the clinic.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">Complete Cost Breakdown</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          To maintain legal access to medical marijuana in Florida, you must budget for three distinct cost categories:
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="border-b border-slate-100 pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-brand-dark">1. Clinical Evaluation Fees</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              Required every 30 weeks (210 days) by the state. This includes your physician consultation, creation of your custom treatment routes, and clinical support. Releaf MD offers straightforward pricing with no hidden charges.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-b border-slate-100 pb-4">
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-brand-dark">2. State Registry ID Card Fee</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              Paid directly to the Florida Department of Health. This fee is <strong>$75.00</strong> and must be paid annually when you apply for or renew your digital registry card.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-brand-dark">3. Retail Dispensary Prices</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              Varies based on the products and brands you choose. Smokable flower typically ranges from $20 to $50 per 1/8th ounce, concentrate cartridges are $30 to $60, and oral edibles are $15 to $25 per package. Most Florida dispensaries offer veteran, senior, and first-time patient discounts to help lower costs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-dark text-white p-8 rounded-2xl border-l-4 border-brand-accent my-10 space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-serif-headline text-brand-mint uppercase">No Hidden Administrative Charges</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            Some high-volume clinics charge patients extra fees to change recommendation routes or increase dosage limits. At Releaf MD, all registry changes, dose updates, and personalized education are included in your standard evaluation fee.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">Evaluation vs. Dispensary Pricing Strategy</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          When budgeting, remember that your clinic evaluation fee secures your clinical legal status, while dispensary purchases are made as needed. We recommend checking dispensary menus online to compare product costs before visiting.
        </p>

        <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 italic">
            Read our <a href="/florida-medical-marijuana-card-guide" class="text-brand-primary font-bold hover:underline">Complete Florida Card Guide</a>.
          </p>
          <a href="/#lead-form" class="bg-brand-accent hover:bg-brand-primary text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-xs uppercase transition-colors shadow-md active-press">
            Schedule Appointment
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
